            "q_1": "What exactly makes your treats \"whole-food\"?",
            "a_1": "<p>Unlike traditional treats filled with \"mystery meats\" and synthetic binders, our treats are made from real, recognizable ingredients in their most natural state. We believe if you can't find the ingredient in a kitchen or a garden, it doesn't belong in your dog's bowl.</p>",
